            "text": "that social distancing matters more than personal hygiene ,",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "and that the growth of infection comes down significantly for moderately high levels of social distancing and hygiene , even in the absence of herd immunity . <S> <P>",
